Step 2 — Validate properties file parsing

Next validate:

/opt/telstra/omega/config/iplogs_spark.properties

Add test:

def validate_properties():
    env_vars = load_env_file("/opt/telstra/omega/omega-common-files/env_subscriber")

    props = load_properties(
        "/opt/telstra/omega/config/iplogs_spark.properties",
        env_vars
    )

    print("Resolved Spark Properties:")
    for k,v in props.items():
        print(f"{k} = {v}")

Expected output example:

spark.kafka.topic.input=OMEGA-TEST-IPLOGS-REQUEST
spark.kafka.group=omega-irqf-iplogs.test.2

This step ensures variable substitution works.

Example substitution:

${ENV}
${DATACENTRE}


