Step 3 — Validate Spark conf dictionary

Now print the final spark_conf before SparkSubmitOperator.

Add:

def validate_spark_conf():
    env_vars = load_env_file("/opt/telstra/omega/omega-common-files/env_subscriber")

    spark_conf = load_properties(
        "/opt/telstra/omega/config/iplogs_spark.properties",
        env_vars
    )

    spark_conf["spark.yarn.queue"] = "query"

    print("Final Spark Conf:")
    for k,v in spark_conf.items():
        print(f"{k}={v}")

This ensures your 40 configs are loaded correctly.


