Step 4 — Validate JAR visibility

Before submitting Spark job we check if all jars exist.

Example paths from your DAG:

/opt/telstra/omega/internetrequestquery/current/irqf.jar
/app/hbase/hbase/lib/*

Add validation task:

import os

def validate_jars():
    jar = "/opt/telstra/omega/internetrequestquery/current/irqf.jar"

    if not os.path.exists(jar):
        raise Exception(f"Jar missing: {jar}")

    print("Jar exists:", jar)


