Step 6 — Run lightweight Spark job with your configs

Now we test SparkSubmitOperator with your configs but not your jar.

Use SparkPi again but with your env + conf.

SparkSubmitOperator(
    task_id="spark_conf_validation",

    conn_id="spark_default",

    application="/app/spark/spark3/examples/jars/spark-examples*.jar",

    java_class="org.apache.spark.examples.SparkPi",

    deploy_mode="cluster",

    conf=spark_conf,

    env_vars=env_vars,

    application_args=["10"]
)

If this works → your Spark configuration is safe.


